long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Removes various types of posts from the youtube subscription page such as live videos, premiering videos, etc. Also has functionality to filter out posts by title.   
I developed this mostly to use for myself so don't expect much in the way of features or bug fixes
